_text = "I'm starting to realize all my memories with friends are somehow tied to camping. Do I just make friends easily with campers or I am the influence?\n\nThis was an odd friend group. It was a combination of friends from highschool and university. I don't think this group would have existed if I hadn't brought them together.\n\nLooking back, this trip was kinda selfish. I liked a boy in that group, so I planned the trip to have an excuse to hangout with him. \n\nI of course wanted an excuse to go camping with the friends I loved, but I still feel a little selfish about the whole thing. Nothing ever happened between me and this said boy, but I'm still glad this trip happened. I made alot of good memories with everyone.\n\nMy best friend was on that trip and I couldn't help but feel like she could read right through my intentions. We never talked about it, but we also never hung out with that group after that."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MeganSittingMemmory, MeganSittingMemmory, false)
